  "text": "Theorem 7 (Asymptotic stability of the gKdV soliton in H 1 , [CITATION_1] ). Let p = 2, 3, 4. For any β > 0, there exists δ = δ(β) > 0 such that the following is true. Let u 0 ∈ H 1 be such that u 0 − Q H 1 ≤ δ. Then, the global solution u of (4) with initial data u 0 satisfies",
